divs: sighting detailssat. oct 22,2011 @10:45pm to 11:40 noticed slow fire orange object\light moving west to east it went out,dissapeared, no sound at all, then another and another ,6 seperate identical objects same path and several minutes apart all no sounds,all seperate objects went out at same place in sky and disapeared from sight.these light objects were low,maybe 500ft above tree level.very intense orange color.realy stuck out in the night sky.i videoed,these objects,but shaky me,nowhere to stabalize camera.i was on my front porch ,faces north,when i first saw the light i thought what the!i remember thinking here we go again,i ve seen strange sightings before right here before usually in the west to east movement. on one occasion i got two creatures on my trailcam not of this world im telling you!
